            BBC News Brexit coverage
            TV coverage after Brexit Secretary Dominic Raab and Work and Pensions Secretary Esther McVey resign over the UK's proposed Brexit agreement. Theresa May has made a statement in the House of Commons on the agreement, telling MPs it was not final, but brought the UK "close to a Brexit deal".This live TV coverage may be interrupted with other news stories
                
